## 7. Analytics Verification
*Open Network Tab -> Filter by Analytics Endpoint.*

1.  **`session_start`**: Fires exactly once when `Promise.all()` resolves.
2.  **`resume_mode_opened`**: Fires when standard resume layout mounts.
3.  **`project_viewed`**: Fires when a Monolith modal opens. Verify `projectId` exists in payload metadata.
4.  **`github_clicked` & `demo_clicked`**: Fires upon CTA clicks inside modals.
5.  **`observatory_found`**: Fires upon entering the `(-150, -150)` radius.
6.  **`contact_submitted`**: Fires only upon successful form validation and submission.
7.  **`lighthouse_activated`**: Fires when the Harbor trigger activates.

